name: inline self-contained spec
description: Demonstrates that source and vocabulary can be specified entirely inline (heredoc) with no external files.
tags: inline, smoke

# Inline vocabulary — replaces an external .merconfig file.
vocab_inline mini: ```
Kind: order is a thing.
Property: id of order is a string.
Property: total of order is a number.
```

# Inline Meridian source — replaces an external .meridian file.
source_inline: ```
---
vocabulary: mini.merconfig
---

To process an order:
  complete.
```

expect_compile: pass
expect_no_unresolved:
expect_workflow_count: 1
expect_workflow_named: ProcessOrder
expect_swift_contains: struct ProcessOrder: MeridianWorkflow
